io.doov.core.dsl.runtime

Class RuntimeField<B,R>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.doov.core.dsl.runtime.RuntimeField<B,R>
  • Type Parameters:
    B - model entry type
    R - field type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    DslField<R>, Readable, FieldInfo, BiConsumer<B,R>, Function<B,R>

    public class RuntimeField<B,R>
extends Object
implements DslField<R>, FieldInfo, Function<B,R>, BiConsumer<B,R>
    Runtime implementation for FieldInfo and DslField. Function.apply(Object) method gets the value of the field from the model. BiConsumer.accept(Object, Object) sets the value of the field to the model.
